34
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:17,100
It's about my father.

35
00:01:23,220 --> 00:01:24,540
Have you found any clues?

36
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:26,420
I haven't found anything

37
00:01:27,350 --> 00:01:28,620
over the past few years,

38
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,420
so I have to try my best

39
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:33,580
to find out the truth.

40
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:42,900
Sister,

41
00:01:43,860 --> 00:01:44,700
he...

42
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:46,580
Why would

43
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:48,860
Uncle Jiang bring this up

44
00:01:48,860 --> 00:01:50,060
at this point?

45
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:52,060
Uncle Jiang has helped us a lot,

46
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,980
but he's a cunning man.

47
00:01:53,980 --> 00:01:54,980
He's up to no good.

48
00:01:54,980 --> 00:01:55,820
Tianyi,

49
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:57,140
I've never said

50
