anything harsh to you,

51
00:01:58,660 --> 00:01:59,500
right?

52
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:01,060
But today,

53
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:02,860
I have to remind you

54
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:04,380
he's our benefactor.

55
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:06,340
