in front of anyone.

56
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:10,100
I'm not slandering him.

57
00:02:10,260 --> 00:02:11,100
I just...

58
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:13,300
I just don't understand.

59
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:14,940
I have to reach my goal,

60
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:16,180
whatever it takes.

61
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:50,980
=Black&White Forest=

62
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:53,980
=Episode 22=

63
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:02,900
Well.

64
00:03:03,340 --> 00:03:04,700
