76
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:28,740
Is it about the case?

77
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:31,420
Stop asking.

78
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:32,780
You have to

79
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,660
tell me the truth,

80
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:35,900
or it's over.

81
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:41,780
Fine.

82
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,460
I'll post it on Moments.

83
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:46,420
I'll tell everyone

84
00:03:46,420 --> 00:03:48,140
