85
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,380
Bin, stop.

86
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:54,620
Chen Yiming killed himself.

87
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:57,180
Dead?

88
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:58,620
No,

89
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,460
we saved him,

90
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:01,220
but the hospital said

91
00:04:01,510 --> 00:04:02,620
he's dangerous.

92
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,580
We don't know

93
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,660
if he can survive.

94
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:07,060
I knew it.

95
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:09,020
When we were having dinner,

96
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:10,700
Xing Liang took a call and left.

97
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:11,860
I knew something happened.

98
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:14,820
Chen Yiming.

99
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,620
Why would Chen Yiming

100
00:04:16,660 --> 00:04:17,500
try to end his life?

101
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:22,780
Did you do what I told you?

102
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:24,780
No.

103
00:04:25,020 --> 00:04:25,980
It's not your fault.

104
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,700
I made a mistake.

105
00:04:29,850 --> 00:04:30,690
Did they punish you?

106
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:34,260
I'll talk to Xing Liang.

107
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:35,660
Bin.

108
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:38,460
I've told you it's not your fault.

109
00:04:38,610 --> 00:04:39,700
It's my fault.

110
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,780
I made a mistake.

111
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:42,460
If you're

112
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:43,820
really guilty,

113
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:44,980
promise me one thing.

114
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:46,980
Okay.

115
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:47,980
I promise.

116
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:49,300
As long as I can...

117
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:51,140
Even if I can't,

118
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:52,860
I'll try my best to do it.

119
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:54,100
Fine.

120
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:55,940
As you know, the case

121
00:04:55,940 --> 00:04:57,020
is very important,

122
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,020
and Mr. Xing has said

123
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:00,580
outsiders can get involved in this.

124
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,700
However,

125
00:05:03,180 --> 00:05:04,300
you're my brother.

126
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,420
I can't turn you down.

127
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,460
So, please don't ask me

128
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:11,460
about the case,

129
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:12,300
okay?

130
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:15,700
I'm busy.

131
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:16,980
Goodbye.

132
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:18,060
- Bin.
- Stop.

133
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:21,500
Bin!

134
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:23,860
Is that a yes or no?

135
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:26,140
Just take the money.

136
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,740
If anything happens

137
00:05:27,940 --> 00:05:29,660
to Uncle Liu, just tell me, okay?

138
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,300
We'll deal with it together.

139
00:05:34,410 --> 00:05:35,740
- What's wrong?
- Nothing.

140
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:36,820
Nothing.

141
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:37,980
What?

142
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:41,260
Uncle Liu fell ill,

143
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:43,380
and Hui wanted to borrow
some money from Man,

144
00:05:44,540 --> 00:05:45,940
but Man wouldn't lend him a penny.

145
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:47,220
If Bao was here,

146
00:05:47,220 --> 00:05:48,580
he wouldn't let this happen.

147
00:05:49,620 --> 00:05:50,940
Didn't I tell you

148
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:53,460
that old man is a rascal?

149
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,940
He looks like a nice person,

150
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:57,700
but he has an evil heart.

151
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:01,500
Well,

152
00:06:01,740 --> 00:06:03,140
ask our brothers to raise

153
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:04,220
some money for him.

154
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:06,100
We've transferred the money to him.

155
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,140
However, think about it.

156
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:08,500
How much

157
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,860
will it cost?

158
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,940
At least we should

159
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:15,500
try our best.

160
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,660
Fine.

161
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,420
Listen, calm down.

162
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:24,500
Bao is not here.

163
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,820
Don't make trouble.

164
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:27,740
Why would I do that?

165
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:30,340
I'll ask him for money.

166
00:06:30,980 --> 00:06:32,580
We've all donated our money.

167
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:33,780
How could he

168
00:06:34,180 --> 00:06:35,060
reject you?

169
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:42,540
Tu Manjiang.

170
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,340
Add some brown sugar.

171
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:11,740
I've told you

172
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,540
Bao isn't here.

173
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:14,980
Yes.

174
00:07:16,620 --> 00:07:17,460
Wait a minute.

175
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:22,660
Bao is not here.

176
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:24,660
It's not up to me.

177
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:27,620
Fine.

178
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,540
I'm coming.

179
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:29,780
Okay.

180
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:30,940
See you later.

181
00:08:30,820 --> 00:08:32,220
I've told you

182
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,300
we need to be careful with him.

183
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:37,180
He sneaked out to see someone.

184
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:38,380
It can't be good.

185
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:40,500
It's too early to say this.

186
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:42,140
You'll eat your words.

187
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:43,940
I'm so curious.

188
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:45,860
What did Uncle Man do?

189
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:47,980
Why do you hate him so much?

190
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,580
He's too pretentious. I don't like it.

191
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:53,620
He's always

192
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:56,020
showing off his knowledge and talent.

193
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,540
Listen, you're too naive.

194
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,820
Why can't you realize he's a pretentious

195
00:09:00,820 --> 00:09:01,700
hypocrite?

196
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:02,700
Fine.

197
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:04,940
You have sharp eyes.

198
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:06,500
I can't wait to see

199
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,500
how you'll reveal his true colors.

200
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:09,740
I'm serious.

201
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:11,540
Think about it.

202
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,500
Now that Bao isn't at the company,

203
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:15,140
he's the one in charge.

204
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:17,180
If he really betrays Bao,

205
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:20,940
it'll be a disaster.

206
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:27,380
Hello.

207
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:32,340
(Guanhai Tea House)

208
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,820
Hello, do you have our membership?

209
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,380
Member?

210
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,020
Well,

211
00:09:42,090 --> 00:09:43,420
we have an appointment.

212
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:45,350
He's on the way, and we'll wait for him.

213
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,900
What's his name?

214
00:09:47,190 --> 00:09:48,030
Well,

215
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:49,460
he's Mr. Wang.

216
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:50,580
Mr. Wang?

217
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,500
We don't have a member
called Mr. Wang.

218
00:09:53,980 --> 00:09:55,500
How's that possible?

219
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,460
Look it up.

220
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,300
I told you he's not reliable,

221
00:09:58,300 --> 00:09:59,140
haven't I?

222
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,660
He didn't believe it.

223
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:03,460
Tell your boss we're here.

224
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:05,310
My boss?

225
00:10:05,830 --> 00:10:07,700
Do you mean Mr. An?

226
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:08,620
Yes.

227
00:10:08,940 --> 00:10:09,860
He invited us

228
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:11,420
to his wine party last time.

229
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:12,540
Just call him.

230
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:14,220
Mr. An told us

231
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:16,060
not to serve anyone who claims

232
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,020
to be his friend.

233
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,700
We know your boss.

234
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:22,180
Please call him.

235
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,660
Sorry. That's the rule.

236
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:28,870
You'll never have a full meal.

237
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:31,660
I just want to take a look.

238
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:33,180
- Hello.
- I'll join your membership.

239
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:35,500
- It's the same.
- Sorry. That's the rule.

240
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:37,700
I'm coming.

241
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:38,540
Don't let them escape.

242
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,300
What's wrong?

243
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:41,300
It's Tuan Island!

244
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,540
Come on. Hit me!

245
00:10:55,700 --> 00:10:56,660
You'll go to jail!

246
00:11:03,380 --> 00:11:04,820
Who started it?

247
00:11:04,820 --> 00:11:05,740
They started it!

248
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:07,820
Ping's son was injured!

249
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:10,100
Mouse Zhou, who the hell are you?

250
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,260
How dare you make a scene?

251
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,740
Did you forget how you begged Bao

252
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:14,940
to spare your life?

253
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:17,900
Luo Tianyi.

254
00:11:18,270 --> 00:11:19,380
Bao is over.

255
00:11:19,690 --> 00:11:20,900
How dare you be so arrogant?

256
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:22,940
Without Bao,

257
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:24,820
do you think a bunch of losers

258
00:11:25,310 --> 00:11:26,550
can keep Tuan Island?

259
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:28,900
Know your place.

260
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:31,460
If I'm satisfied,

261
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:33,540
maybe I'll offer you a job.

262
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,620
How dare you say that?

263
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:37,140
Listen,

264
00:11:37,420 --> 00:11:38,580
you have more people.

265
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:40,340
Otherwise, I'll tear your mouth!

266
00:11:42,580 --> 00:11:44,140
Bao is accused of murder.

267
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:45,900
Even if he can survive,

268
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:47,180
he'll spend

269
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,580
the rest of his life in jail.

270
00:11:49,460 --> 00:11:50,300
Do you think

271
00:11:50,450 --> 00:11:52,060
he can have your back?

272
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:03,500
Tianyi.

273
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:04,580
Stop.

274
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:08,500
Mouse,

275
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:09,740
I suggest you

276
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:10,860
know your place.

277
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:12,780
You don't deserve
to get Bao's attention.

278
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:14,260
Listen,

279
00:12:14,580 --> 00:12:16,540
if you come here again,

280
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:18,180
I'll break your legs.

281
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:19,980
- Understand?
- Yes.

282
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:20,940
Get lost!

283
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,140
Stop looking!

284
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:26,620
Get lost!

285
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:29,220
Get lost!

286
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:31,820
Well, was Mouse Zhou

287
00:12:31,820 --> 00:12:33,620
telling the truth?

288
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,980
Will Bao come back?

289
00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:37,980
Nonsense.

290
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,620
If Bao can't come back,

291
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:40,860
they'll make trouble every day.

292
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,640
Our business will be ruined!

293
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,260
After this fight,

294
00:12:45,570 --> 00:12:46,540
no customers will come.

295
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:48,500
We should close our stores.

296
00:12:59,770 --> 00:13:00,610
What happened?

297
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:02,980
We had a fight with

298
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,520
some troublemakers.

