00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:07,620
I've told you

300
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:09,100
this is a critical time,

301
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:11,180
and you need to stay calm.

302
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:12,550
Stay calm?

303
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:14,980
Answer me. How can we stay calm?

304
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:16,980
They'll only hit us harder

305
00:13:16,980 --> 00:13:18,620
if we hold back. Do we have a choice?

306
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:19,660
Listen,

307
00:13:20,060 --> 00:13:21,780
if they cause trouble again,

308
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:23,620
I'll take care of them for good!

309
00:13:23,620 --> 00:13:24,740
Luo Tianyi.

310
00:13:25,220 --> 00:13:26,300
Can you think twice

311
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,900
before taking action?

312
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:28,900
You're so reckless.

313
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,180
You'll get us into big trouble!

314
00:13:30,180 --> 00:13:31,780
How are you going to explain it to Bao?

315
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:34,300
If I don't help the neighbors
in trouble,

316
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:36,260
how can I face Bao?

317
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,940
Fine. Whatever.

318
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:41,100
I can't stop you.

319
00:13:41,220 --> 00:13:42,620
Anyway, I've warned you.

320
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:44,980
Don't act like we're bullying you.

321
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:46,500
Fine, let me ask you a question.

322
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:48,540
Where were you

323
00:13:48,730 --> 00:13:50,070
when they were in trouble?

324
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:51,300
I...

325
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,860
I went to the bank to meet a client.

326
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:55,700
What a coincidence.

327
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:56,980
You left right before they came.

328
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:58,100
Tianyi!

329
00:13:58,620 --> 00:13:59,460
Shut up.

330
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:02,940
At this point,

331
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,340
we should stick together
and deal with our enemy.

332
00:14:06,060 --> 00:14:07,260
Stop arguing with our people.

333
00:14:07,700 --> 00:14:08,780
They'll laugh at us.

334
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,060
Tianyi was just

335
00:14:13,190 --> 00:14:14,300
too angry.

336
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:16,660
Please don't blame him.

337
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:19,780
Tianyi,

338
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:21,860
apologize to Uncle Man.

339
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:34,700
Don't be angry.

340
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:43,820
(Tang Zheng Hotel Supplies)

341
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,060
Look at you.

342
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:58,260
You really

343
00:14:58,260 --> 00:15:00,140
pissed Uncle Man off.

344
00:15:01,380 --> 00:15:03,180
Still angry?

345
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:04,820
Fine.

346
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:07,580
You can yell at me as you want.

347
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:09,940
Hey, bro,

348
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:11,260
which side are you on?

349
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:13,660
Why did you ask me to apologize?

350
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:16,860
He's an indifferent bystander.

351
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:17,900
Why did you help him?

352
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:19,140
I was helping you.

353
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:21,220
If Uncle Man leaves,

354
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:22,620
who will deal with

355
00:15:22,620 --> 00:15:23,460
this mess?

356
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:24,860
Can you?

357
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:31,900
I know you don't like Uncle Man,

358
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:33,700
but you have to admit

359
00:15:33,940 --> 00:15:35,500
he's really capable.

360
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:37,740
Bao is in detention.

361
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:40,140
If Uncle Man quits his job and leaves,

362
00:15:40,860 --> 00:15:41,900
it'll be a disaster.

363
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:44,020
We don't know if he's innocent.

364
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:48,820
Why did you believe he went to the bank?

365
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:52,380
You don't have evidence,

366
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:53,660
so don't tell others about it.

367
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:55,820
Many people are watching us

368
00:15:55,820 --> 00:15:56,780
right now.

369
00:15:57,260 --> 00:15:58,780
They want us
to fight against each other.

370
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:05,900
Why are they

371
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,260
closing their stores now?

372
00:16:07,940 --> 00:16:09,380
They usually go home at night.

373
00:16:09,980 --> 00:16:11,580
Business has been bad,

374
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:14,780
and Mouse Zhou smashed the market.

375
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,420
Who dares to come?

376
00:16:16,660 --> 00:16:17,860
We can

377
00:16:18,860 --> 00:16:20,020
think of this

378
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:21,980
as an opportunity
to replace the old stuff.

379
00:16:22,260 --> 00:16:24,460
And maybe they'll attract new customers.

380
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,060
Huh.

381
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:30,780
Do you think they're as rich as you?

382
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:34,700
They're making a living here

383
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:36,460
because they don't have money.

384
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:41,420
They can only afford
to repair the broken things.

385
00:16:42,540 --> 00:16:44,020
I'm not asking them to pay for it.

386
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:45,740
I'll pay, okay?

387
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,500
How much do you have?

388
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:56,900
What do you want?

389
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:04,820
This one.

390
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:07,860
I know it's wrong.

391
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:09,740
I'm doing this for my kid!

392
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:11,620
Besides, I only want to sell my stuff.

393
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:12,700
Am I wrong?

394
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,220
I didn't say that.

395
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:17,260
Fine. You don't want to be the bad guy.

396
00:17:17,620 --> 00:17:18,780
I'll do it!

397
00:17:19,130 --> 00:17:20,580
Where are you going?

398
00:17:20,580 --> 00:17:22,180
I'm going out!

399
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:23,460
You...

400
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:24,900
Where are you going?

401
00:17:27,740 --> 00:17:28,740
Ping?

402
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:32,500
You live next door to Hui?

403
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,620
(Share Transfer Agreement)

404
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:35,300
We're neighbors.

405
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,240
Yes.

406
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:47,380
Qi Hanchen is so cunning.

407
00:17:47,940 --> 00:17:49,420
He's trying to steal our shares.

408
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:51,260
Luckily, we discovered it early.

409
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:52,940
Only Auntie Chen signed the deal.

410
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,020
The other vendors haven't decided.

411
00:17:56,660 --> 00:17:58,020
Since Bao was arrested,

412
00:17:58,580 --> 00:17:59,940
everyone has been anxious.

413
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,780
Besides, they've been

414
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:03,740
making a scene

415
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:05,900
and spreading bad rumors about Bao.

416
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:08,140
They're offering the best price

417
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:09,940
to reassure people

418
00:18:09,940 --> 00:18:11,940
and using preferential ranks

419
00:18:12,580 --> 00:18:14,180
to arouse their eagerness.

420
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:18,580
It's brilliant.

421
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:20,820
He's playing dirty.

422
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:21,780
How can you defend him?

423
00:18:22,460 --> 00:18:24,380
I'm just being objective.

424
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:26,060
The priority

425
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,820
is to figure out how to deal with it.

426
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:28,860
We can't let them

427
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:30,580
acquire the vendors' shares.

428
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:33,820
I've sent people

429
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:34,780
to keep an eye on them.

430
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:35,860
If they sell their shares...

431
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:39,060
Do you want to go to jail too?

432
00:18:40,540 --> 00:18:42,420
We can gain their sympathy,

433
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:44,060
but they own the shares.

434
00:18:44,580 --> 00:18:45,780
They have the right

435
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:47,900
to decide what's best for them.

436
00:18:49,300 --> 00:18:50,140
Man,

437
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,460
what's your opinion?

438
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:57,060
I think the best solution right now

439
00:18:58,340 --> 00:18:59,620
is to cooperate with Qi Hanchen.

440
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:01,900
What? What's wrong with you?

441
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:05,860
They didn't want

442
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:07,340
to sell their shares

443
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:08,660
because Bao was here.

444
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:11,340
He'll be detained for a while.

445
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:13,500
The more unsettled the vendors are,

446
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,860
the more shares

447
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:16,900
will be sold.

448
00:19:17,620 --> 00:19:18,660
If Qi Hanchen

449
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:21,700
gets all their shares,

450
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:24,420
it'll be a big threat

451
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:26,460
for us.

452
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:31,620
Arrange a meeting with him.

453
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:48,660
Ms. Wen,

454
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:51,420
maybe we should think it through.

455
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:54,180
Bao's bottom line
is to keep Tuan Island.

456
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:56,660
We have to talk to him in person.

457
00:19:57,620 --> 00:19:58,820
I want to see

458
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:01,260
how greedy he is.

459
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:07,940
Xing, I'm impressed.

460
00:20:08,710 --> 00:20:10,060
A major suspect

461
00:20:10,490 --> 00:20:12,420
nearly killed himself

462
00:20:12,700 --> 00:20:14,100
under your watch.

463
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:16,220
What the hell have you done?

464
00:20:17,580 --> 00:20:18,980
It's my fault.

465
00:20:19,710 --> 00:20:20,900
I can accept any punishment

466
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:21,860
except for suspension.

467
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:23,580
I must solve the case.

468
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:26,350
Listen, you're so lucky.

469
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:28,740
He's still alive.

470
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,340
We'll

471
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:38,270
accept the advice your team submitted.

472
00:20:39,790 --> 00:20:40,630
In addition,

473
00:20:42,380 --> 00:20:43,340
I went to

474
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:44,300
the Provincial Department.

475
00:20:45,860 --> 00:20:46,700
The leader said

476
00:20:47,530 --> 00:20:48,930
according to the current statement

477
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:50,230
and relevant evidence,

478
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:52,260
the gun case

479
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:53,540
should be closed.

480
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:57,340
There's still so much doubt.

481
00:20:57,340 --> 00:20:58,300
Closed?

482
00:20:58,300 --> 00:20:59,420
Are you kidding me?

483
00:20:59,420 --> 00:21:00,420
Calm down.

484
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,020
Do you know how many people

485
00:21:03,020 --> 00:21:03,900
are on this case?

486
00:21:05,380 --> 00:21:06,540
Don't you know

487
00:21:06,540 --> 00:21:07,660
how stressed I am?

488
00:21:08,230 --> 00:21:09,070
Besides,

489
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:11,140
I'm not asking you to stop.

490
00:21:11,870 --> 00:21:13,620
The case is closed,

491
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:16,410
but there won't be
an awards ceremony for now.

492
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:18,420
The task force will continue
to investigate it.

493
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:20,140
Are you happy now?

494
00:21:20,740 --> 00:21:21,620
Why should I be happy?

495
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:22,900
We deserve it.

496
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:26,100
Don't get carried away.

497
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:29,540
I've tried my best to get what you need,

498
00:21:29,740 --> 00:21:31,020
but you must promise me,

499
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:32,540
if you want to solve the case,

500
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:33,780
don't go too far,

501
00:21:34,180 --> 00:21:35,020
okay?

502
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,210
Last time, you nearly

503
00:21:37,210 --> 00:21:38,100
ended up in prison.

504
00:21:38,260 --> 00:21:39,620
Don't let it happen again.

505
00:21:40,330 --> 00:21:41,300
Got it.

506
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:43,140
It won't happen again.

507
00:21:45,850 --> 00:21:46,690
Xing.

508
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:50,100
You know what you're doing,

509
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:51,300
and I won't stop you.

510
00:21:52,140 --> 00:21:52,980
However,

511
00:21:53,450 --> 00:21:54,580
at this point,

512
00:21:55,580 --> 00:21:56,420
if you really

513
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,980
want to dig into it,

514
00:21:59,020 --> 00:21:59,940
it won't

515
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:03,060
just be a criminal case.

516
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,580
I believe you know

517
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,200
what's behind the case.

518
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:13,420
Xuan,

519
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:15,700
it was my father

520
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:17,140
and Uncle Wen's favorite wine.

521
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,500
They'd

522
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,980
have a drink

523
00:22:21,580 --> 00:22:22,780
with some small dishes

524
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:24,260
from time to time.

525
00:22:26,620 --> 00:22:27,740
They could talk all night.

526
00:22:27,740 --> 00:22:29,780
I still don't know

527
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:32,260
why they had so much to talk about.

528
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:35,980
Do you know?

529
00:22:36,780 --> 00:22:38,140
There was a time

530
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:39,780
when my mother had a problem

531
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:41,740
with Uncle Wen

532
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:42,780
because of this.

533
00:22:44,460 --> 00:22:45,940
You were right about it.

534
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:47,940
I remember my mother and Auntie Wu

535
00:22:48,040 --> 00:22:49,710
could also talk all night.

536
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:52,100
Back then, I also had a good time

537
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:54,140
because I overheard many gossips.

538
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,420
Really?

539
00:23:00,340 --> 00:23:01,260
Xuan.

540
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:03,500
You talked about our past last time.

541
00:23:04,580 --> 00:23:06,220
I've been thinking about it.

542
00:23:08,460 --> 00:23:10,020
Our friendship

543
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,580
is very precious.

544
00:23:12,980 --> 00:23:14,220
You can never have enough money.

545
00:23:14,740 --> 00:23:16,020
If we become enemies

546
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:17,580
because of money,

547
00:23:18,380 --> 00:23:19,580
it'll be so not worth it.

548
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:22,340
Well,

549
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:23,580
let's forget about

550
00:23:24,820 --> 00:23:25,700
what happened.

551
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:27,900
Here's to you.

552
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:29,740
I apologize

553
00:23:30,140 --> 00:23:31,500
for what I did.

554
00:23:32,340 --> 00:23:34,260
You don't have to do this.

555
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:36,120
Our families are old friends.

556
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:37,580
I won't hold a grudge against you.

557
00:23:45,180 --> 00:23:47,300
That'd be great.

558
00:23:52,620 --> 00:23:53,940
To express my gratitude,

559
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:55,940
I've prepared a gift.

560
00:24:08,140 --> 00:24:09,460
(MorningStar Investment, MOU)

561
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:15,020
Then I'll

562
00:24:15,460 --> 00:24:16,420
take this.

563
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:19,480
Come on.

564
00:24:20,330 --> 00:24:21,340
Here's to you.

565
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:35,300
Drinking together

566
00:24:35,660 --> 00:24:37,620
is much more interesting

567
00:24:38,220 --> 00:24:39,220
than drinking alone.

568
00:24:40,340 --> 00:24:41,740
We're partners now.

569
00:24:42,180 --> 00:24:43,820
We'll have many opportunities

570
00:24:44,020 --> 00:24:45,300
to drink together.

571
00:24:46,540 --> 00:24:47,380
Yes.

572
00:24:48,300 --> 00:24:49,300
When

573
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,340
Bao is free,

574
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:52,700
I believe

575
00:24:53,340 --> 00:24:54,500
we'll have more time

576
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:55,460
to drink together.

577
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,340
That's right.

578
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:02,660
I was too impatient.

579
00:25:06,380 --> 00:25:07,220
We'll

580
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:09,100
save this wine.

581
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:10,940
When Bao is released,

582
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:13,340
we'll drink it for the celebration.

583
00:25:14,060 --> 00:25:14,940
Xuan, don't worry.

584
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:17,060
I won't let you wait for too long.

585
00:25:20,540 --> 00:25:21,460
(Binjiang Detention Center)

586
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:22,660
(Relevant)
What took him so long?

587
00:25:22,660 --> 00:25:23,580
(Personnel Only)

588
00:25:23,580 --> 00:25:24,420
Don't worry.

589
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:25,900
It's about time.

590
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:29,180
The police said they lacked evidence.

591
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:31,140
As long as there's no new evidence,

592
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:32,420
Bao will be alright.

593
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:52,500
Don't do this.

